    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Separate residences for guests, particularly when on a private estate or monastery and maintained specifically for receiving visitors. Houses used to provide lodging for paying guests; sometimes used for houses that are used specifically for the entertainment of guests.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
